first_para: Shahrar Ali (['ʃɑːrɑː ɑː'liː]) is the Deputy Leader of the Green Party of England and Wales alongside Amelia Womack.

full.extract:
Shahrar Ali (['ʃɑːrɑː ɑː'liː]) is the Deputy Leader of the Green Party of England and Wales alongside Amelia Womack.
He was elected in September 2014 at the Green Party conference in Aston, Birmingham.
full.title: Shahrar Ali
